snippet.title: Space Chicks - Official Trailer - November 21
snippet.description:
Space Chicks is an Endless Platformer with ultra simple controls, amazing space physics and lots of fun headed to be released for iOS on November 21st.

The Bad Guys have kidnapped all the Chicks in the Universe! You'll be controlling a small astronaut, Hero, to rescue and save as many as you can!

Powered by Unity3d
